    "body": "Currently we can only set environment variables from the compiler config file. This allows us to prepend to paths.\r\n\r\nE.G.\r\n```\r\ncompilers:\r\n- compiler:\r\n  spec: gcc@7.3.0\r\n  environment:\r\n    prepend-path:\r\n      PATH: /usr/bin/gnu/extra_bin\r\n...\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis appears to be particularly relevant for PGI compilers.",
